    "longBusinessSummary": "Hoa Tho Textile - Garment Joint Stock Corporation produces, imports, exports, and trades in clothes, fabrics, fibers, equipment, and raw materials for the garment and textile industry in Vietnam, China, the United States, Japan, Africa, Sweden, and internationally. It operates in two segments, Garment and Yarn. The company provides garments for export markets, such as veston, pants, workwear, jackets/outerwear, and knitwear; and uniforms for elementary, secondary, and high school students, as well as business uniforms; and men and women fashion products. It also offers TC, double/three, CD, and CVC yarns. The company was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in Da Nang, Vietnam. Hoa Tho Textile - Garment Joint Stock Corporation operates as a subsidiary of Vietnam National Textile and Garment Group.",
